# Project — basics

- Change only what the task requires; no drive-by refactors of unrelated modules.
- Match neighboring files (imports, types, comment depth).
- Stack overview and directory tree — root `AGENTS.md`.
- Feature details and regressions — `docs/` (`docs/04-features.md`, `docs/qa/`).
- App Python package: `backend.*` imports from the repository root (`PYTHONPATH` = repo root).
